remarks.span: 此类实现了 "MSBuild" 任务，该任务将子项目文件移交给要生成的 MSBuild 引擎。

span.span: This class implements the "MSBuild" task, which hands off child project files to the MSBuild engine to be built.

remarks.span: 标记为 RunInMTA，因为 MSBuild 任务不应在生成它们的 RequestBuilder 的线程上运行。

span.span: Marked RunInMTA because there is no reason MSBuild tasks should run on a thread other than that of the RequestBuilder which spawned them.

summary.span: 如果为 true，则会（对于每个项目）为每个目标调用一次引擎，而不是（对于每个项目）调用一次引擎以生成所有目标。

span.span: When this is true, instead of calling the engine once to build all the targets (for each project), we would call the engine once per target (for each project).

summary.span: 这样做的好处是，如果一个目标事变，仍可继续生成剩余的目标。

span.span: The benefit of this is that if one target fails, you can still continue with the remaining targets.

span.span: if the MSBuild task invokes each target in the list passed to MSBuild one at a time; if the MSBuild task invokes all targets in the list at the same time.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 如果将此属性设置为，则可 `true` 保证即使之前调用的目标失败，也会调用后续目标。Setting this property to `true` guarantees that subsequent targets are invoked even if previously invoked targets failed. 否则，生成错误将停止调用所有后续目标。Otherwise, a build error would stop invocation of all subsequent targets. 默认值是 `false`。The default value is `false`.
